<abstract><t>This document specifies IS-IS autoconfiguration mechanisms.  The key components are IS-IS System ID self-generation, duplication detection, and duplication resolution.  These mechanisms provide limited IS-IS functions and are therefore suitable for networks where plug-and-play configuration is expected.</t></abstract>
